# Keep build contexts small and reproducible: never ship host build output or
# local databases into an image. Source is bind-mounted for the build/test and
# apk-builder services, so these are only excluded from the copied contexts
# (server image) and to speed up context transfer.
.git
**/target
**/build
**/.dart_tool
**/.idea
app/.flutter-plugins-dependencies
**/*.iml
*.db
*.db-journal
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
server/goober-dev.db
.lavish
